re":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:30:56.000Z","msg":"魚與熊掌係兼得唔到架，要全面管治就唔好諗咩國際金融中心。支共又唔係唔知自己個朵臭，香港冇得再自治，邊個信你支共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:32:54.000Z","msg":"佢地咁撚死蠢<br />\n我等緊佢地仆街嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜都要控制 等睇輸到底褲都冇埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:36:19.000Z","msg":"睇以前上海就知咩事，夾硬搶返來嘅只會變垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eadd350ab80c3f2872e25eb661ca8edf542da5a3","tid":2433370,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5872b48ad9632721716fb0712de0dda9ea06bea8","tid":2433370,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"609d32515ccf4c1426ccb01042549a0c224a815e","tid":2433370,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:33:45.000Z","msg":"一國兩制高度自治港人自治五十年不變<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:34:54.000Z","msg":"得返一國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:36:20.000Z","msg":"港人治港先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b39aa6e42ca2c761748b6f80de6de575bc4e6fc4","tid":2433370,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:37:14.000Z","msg":"李克強：堅決防範和遏制外部勢力干預港澳事務<br />\n<br />\n第十三屆全國人民代表大會第四次會議早上在北京開幕。<br />\n<br />\n國務院總理李克強發表的工作報告提到，要繼續全面準確貫徹「一國兩制」、「港人治港」、「澳人治澳」、高度自治的方針，完善特別行政區憲法和基本法實施相關制度和機制，落實特別行政區維護國家安全的法律制度和執行機制。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，堅決防範和遏制外部勢力干預港澳事務，支持港澳發展經濟、改善民生，保持香港、澳門長期繁榮穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578859-20210305.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578859-20210305.htm&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=734ed31c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578859-20210305.htm&h=5c6ef7ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578859-20210305.htm</a>"},{"pid":"770f69a6da2ed060796ae71685048cf401772486","tid":2433370,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eadd350ab80c3f2872e25eb661ca8edf542da5a3","tid":2433370,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5872b48ad9632721716fb0712de0dda9ea06bea8","tid":2433370,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"609d32515ccf4c1426ccb01042549a0c224a815e","tid":2433370,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:33:45.000Z","msg":"一國兩制高度自治港人自治五十年不變<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:34:54.000Z","msg":"得返一國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:36:20.000Z","msg":"港人治港先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:37:28.000Z","msg":"不嬲當777同班黑警係支那狗，港條毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8760751107972d45dbe101d51d86931848dc9a7e","tid":2433370,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:38:29.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家垃圾口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c09acee261111daf1256094264f58067bd3de9","tid":2433370,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47d6d0749f864fea3eedd92edabd8fa5ef3b8451","tid":2433370,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"re